These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, iced-tea, almond-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, video-games, writing, traveling
1. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking 7up and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
3. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking 7up##7
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | almond-milk       | milk | 7up        |
| Hobby      | writing  | video-games | traveling        | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, chinchilla, cat, ferret
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, baseball, swimming, parkour
1. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere between the person who's sport is swimming and the owner of the cat##7
2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
3. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is baseball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | cat | chinchilla       | ferret         | lizard     |
| Sport   | baseball   | parkour | swimming | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, martial-arts, zombie, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, disco, hip-hop, gospel
1. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of gospel is somewhere between the fan of disco and the fan of jazz##7
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
4. the fan of jazz is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the person watching martial-arts movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | western | zombie | sports  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | jazz  | gospel   | disco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, filmmaking, video-games, gardening
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, water-polo, biathlon, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | drawing | gardening       | video-games |
| Sport   | water-polo      | rowing   | biathlon | soccer  |

