.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, traveling, card-games, puzzles
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, australian, pakistani, french
1. the french is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
2. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the french is somewhere between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
5. the french is on the left of the pakistani##1
6. the australian is somewhere to the left of the french##5
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | card-games | magic-tricks   | puzzles | traveling |
| Nationality   | dutch      | australian | french      | pakistani |

