.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, fanta, lemonade, iced-tea
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, polish, mexican, egyptian
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the mexican##1
2. the mexican is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the polish is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
6. the egyptian is somewhere between the canadian and the polish##7
7. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | fanta | juice      | lemonade | iced-tea     |
| Nationality   | canadian    | egyptian | polish   | mexican |

