.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, pomegranate, zucchini, nectarine
There are 4 different nationalities: american, polish, indonesian, italian
1. the american is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the polish##1
3. the person eating nectarine is on the far left or far right##3
4. the italian is somewhere between the person eating spinach and the person eating zucchini##7
5. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the person eating zucchini##5
6. the italian is on the left or right of the indonesian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | nectarine    | spinach   | pomegranate | zucchini  |
| Nationality   | american | indonesian | italian    | polish |

