.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, russian, mexican, pakistani
4 different pets are kept: snake, guinea-pig, chinchilla, ferret
1. the russian is not the owner of the ferret##6
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
3. the pakistani is the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the mexican is somewhere between the pakistani and the indian##7
5. the russian is on the left of the indian##1
6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | mexican | russian | indian |
| Pet           | chinchilla   | ferret    | snake       | guinea-pig  |

