2. the videographer is on the right of the social-worker##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
4. the social-worker is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
5. the videographer is somewhere between the fan of salsa and the writer##7
6. the fan of metal is somewhere to the right of the fan of ambient##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | pilot | social-worker | videographer | writer |
| Music-Genre   | salsa         | ambient      | dubstep | metal            |

