2. the person watching animation movies is not the owner of the goat##6
3. the owner of the lizard is not the person watching romance movies##6
4. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
5. the person watching documentary movies is the owner of the ferret##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
