.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, satire, superhero, zombie
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, r&b, electronic
1. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan of hip-hop##5
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the fan of indie is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person watching action movies is between the person watching satire movies and the fan of indie##2
6. the fan of r&b is somewhere between the fan of indie and the person watching satire movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | action | satire | superhero   |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | r&b      | hip-hop      | electronic |

