3. the person who's sport is soccer is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##5
6. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is hiking##7

