2. the person who's hobby is photography is the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the taxi is the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is not the person driving the skateboard##6
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the person who's hobby is reading##7
7. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | photography | camping | chess | reading |
| Transport   | ship   | snowmobile      | skateboard        | taxi  |

