1. the fan of disco is in an even position##4
2. the fan of funk is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the fan of ambient##7
3. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
4. the fan of ambient is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the fan of disco##5
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | hot-chocolate | lemonade | soy-milk   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | ambient   | funk | disco |

