.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, horse, pony
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, airplane, tram
1. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the person driving the car and the owner of the goat##7
2. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
5. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | goat    | horse | pony     | chinchilla |
| Transport   | airplane | tram  | roller | car |

 